<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>501</hymn_number>
<title>KILVENG ZUNGZAL HNA CH501</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Cung chin kan biak Pathian samhri sihnak thawngin thih hlan leng ti
 dingin fonh nan si bangin, Khrihfa inn-chungkhar tha, Kom hawi phai len
 awkin, Thluachuah cung vanni za hmu ko u.

[C1]
   Atu thit-umnak hi chan chung nguh in fek seh, Maw Bawipa na dawtnak
   in run tem hna! An i dawtnak thuk in hram thla kho ve dingah, Na Thiang
   thlarau in kilveng zungzal hna.

[V2]
 Nunnak hawikom sung bik hngatchan tlak si u law hrin nu sorpa thlua
 chuah in pe ko hna seh, Nunnak lam har chungah zumhtlak in i daw u,
 Bawipa dawtnak muihmel langhter u.

[C2]
   Atu thit-umnak hi chan chung nguh in fek seh, Maw Bawipa na dawtnak
   in run tem hna! An i dawtnak thuk in hram thla kho ve dingah, Na Thiang
   thlarau in kilveng zungzal hna.

[V3]
 Hmaizah le zawnruahnak Khrihfa nuncan sung bik nannih innchungkhar ah
 leng ve zungzal seh, Leng le val zohchunh awk hmailei lam-sialtu ah,
 Bawipa nih in daw zungzal hna seh.

[C3]
   Atu thit-umnak hi chan chung nguh in fek seh, Maw Bawipa na dawtnak
   in run tem hna! An i dawtnak thuk in hram thla kho ve dingah, Na Thiang
   thlarau in kilveng zungzal hna.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
</song>